NAME flatbuffers
VERSION 22.9.29
SYSTEM_LIBS ALLOW
SOURCE URL https://github.com/google/flatbuffers/archive/refs/tags/v22.9.29.tar.gz
BUILD_SYSTEM CMAKE
CMAKE_DEFINE FLATBUFFERS_BUILD_TESTS=OFF
CMAKE_DEFINE FLATBUFFERS_BUILD_FLATC=OFF
TARGET flatbuffers::flatbuffers STATIC lib/libflatbuffers.a INTERFACE include
